NAME
    Dist::Zilla::Plugin::MojibakeTests - Release tests for source encoding

VERSION
    version 0.5

SYNOPSIS
    In dist.ini:

        [MojibakeTests]

DESCRIPTION
    This is an extension of Dist::Zilla::Plugin::InlineFiles, providing the
    following file:

        xt/release/mojibake.t - a standard Test::Mojibake test

AUTHOR
    Stanislaw Pusep <stas@sysd.org>

